@startuml
actor Doctor
participant "Flutter Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Express API" as API
participant "Doctor Controller" as DoctorController
participant "PatientProfile" as PatientStore
participant "Doctor Update Notification Service" as NotifyService
participant "Realtime Notification Service" as Realtime
database "MongoDB" as Mongo
participant "Patient SSE Client" as PatientClient

Doctor -> Frontend : Update dosage / report / review / instructions
Frontend -> API : PUT/PATCH doctor endpoint\nBearer JWT
API -> DoctorController : authenticate + validate
DoctorController -> Mongo : load doctor and patient
DoctorController -> PatientStore : update patient data
PatientStore -> Mongo : persist PatientProfile changes
Mongo --> PatientStore : saved

DoctorController -> NotifyService : createDoctorUpdateNotification(...)
NotifyService -> Mongo : insert Notification(type=DOCTOR_UPDATE)
Mongo --> NotifyService : created notification
NotifyService -> Realtime : publishNotificationToUser(...)
Realtime --> PatientClient : SSE event doctor_update / notification

DoctorController --> API : ApiResponse
API --> Frontend : success
@enduml
